				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Automaton in the Underdark tower can give to player (or drop) a magic ring. While wearing this ring, a secret hidden button appears in the tower's teleport. That button leads to undeground lab. This PAD was added to explain to player that wearing the ring led to button to appear."
